58#include <stdio.h>
59
60#include <openssl/asn1t.h>
61#include <openssl/conf.h>
62#include <openssl/err.h>
63#include <openssl/obj.h>
64#include <openssl/x509v3.h>
65
66
67static void *v2i_POLICY_MAPPINGS(const X509V3_EXT_METHOD *method,
68 X509V3_CTX *ctx, STACK_OF(CONF_VALUE) *nval);
69static STACK_OF(CONF_VALUE) *
70i2v_POLICY_MAPPINGS(const X509V3_EXT_METHOD *method, void *pmps,
71 STACK_OF(CONF_VALUE) *extlist);
72
73const X509V3_EXT_METHOD v3_policy_mappings = {
74 NID_policy_mappings, 0,
75 ASN1_ITEM_ref(POLICY_MAPPINGS),
76 0,0,0,0,
77 0,0,
78 i2v_POLICY_MAPPINGS,
79 v2i_POLICY_MAPPINGS,
80 0,0,
81 NULL
82};
83
84ASN1_SEQUENCE(POLICY_MAPPING) = {
85 ASN1_SIMPLE(POLICY_MAPPING, issuerDomainPolicy, ASN1_OBJECT),
86 ASN1_SIMPLE(POLICY_MAPPING, subjectDomainPolicy, ASN1_OBJECT)
87} ASN1_SEQUENCE_END(POLICY_MAPPING)
88
89ASN1_ITEM_TEMPLATE(POLICY_MAPPINGS) =
90 ASN1_EX_TEMPLATE_TYPE(ASN1_TFLG_SEQUENCE_OF, 0, POLICY_MAPPINGS,
91 POLICY_MAPPING)
92ASN1_ITEM_TEMPLATE_END(POLICY_MAPPINGS)
93
94IMPLEMENT_ASN1_ALLOC_FUNCTIONS(POLICY_MAPPING)
95
96
97static STACK_OF(CONF_VALUE) *
98i2v_POLICY_MAPPINGS(const X509V3_EXT_METHOD *method, void *a,
99 STACK_OF(CONF_VALUE) *ext_list)
100{
101 POLICY_MAPPINGS *pmaps = a;
102 POLICY_MAPPING *pmap;
103 size_t i;
104 char obj_tmp1[80];
105 char obj_tmp2[80];
106 for(i = 0; i < sk_POLICY_MAPPING_num(pmaps); i++) {
107 pmap = sk_POLICY_MAPPING_value(pmaps, i);
108 i2t_ASN1_OBJECT(obj_tmp1, 80, pmap->issuerDomainPolicy);
109 i2t_ASN1_OBJECT(obj_tmp2, 80, pmap->subjectDomainPolicy);
110 X509V3_add_value(obj_tmp1, obj_tmp2, &ext_list);
111 }
112 return ext_list;
113}
114
115static void *v2i_POLICY_MAPPINGS(const X509V3_EXT_METHOD *method,
116 X509V3_CTX *ctx, STACK_OF(CONF_VALUE) *nval)
117{
118 POLICY_MAPPINGS *pmaps;
119 POLICY_MAPPING *pmap;
120 ASN1_OBJECT *obj1, *obj2;
121 CONF_VALUE *val;
122 size_t i;
123
124 if(!(pmaps = sk_POLICY_MAPPING_new_null())) {
125 OPENSSL_PUT_ERROR(X509V3, ERR_R_MALLOC_FAILURE);
126 return NULL;
127 }
128
129 for(i = 0; i < sk_CONF_VALUE_num(nval); i++) {
130 val = sk_CONF_VALUE_value(nval, i);
131 if(!val->value || !val->name) {
132 sk_POLICY_MAPPING_pop_free(pmaps, POLICY_MAPPING_free);
133 OPENSSL_PUT_ERROR(X509V3, X509V3_R_INVALID_OBJECT_IDENTIFIER);
134 X509V3_conf_err(val);
135 return NULL;
136 }
137 obj1 = OBJ_txt2obj(val->name, 0);
138 obj2 = OBJ_txt2obj(val->value, 0);
139 if(!obj1 || !obj2) {
140 sk_POLICY_MAPPING_pop_free(pmaps, POLICY_MAPPING_free);
141 OPENSSL_PUT_ERROR(X509V3, X509V3_R_INVALID_OBJECT_IDENTIFIER);
142 X509V3_conf_err(val);
143 return NULL;
144 }
145 pmap = POLICY_MAPPING_new();
146 if (!pmap) {
147 sk_POLICY_MAPPING_pop_free(pmaps, POLICY_MAPPING_free);
148 OPENSSL_PUT_ERROR(X509V3, ERR_R_MALLOC_FAILURE);
149 return NULL;
150 }
151 pmap->issuerDomainPolicy = obj1;
152 pmap->subjectDomainPolicy = obj2;
153 sk_POLICY_MAPPING_push(pmaps, pmap);
154 }
155 return pmaps;
156}
